description: Deedle implements an efficient and robust frame and series data structures for manipulating with structured data. It supports handling of missing values, aggregations, grouping, joining, statistical functions and more. For frames and series with ordered indices (such as time series), automatic alignment is also available. This package installs core Deedle package, together with an R type provider plugin which makes it possible to pass data frames and time series between R and Deedle
